; init.srv — LinFBB (F6FBB) server identity for the pdn-bbs interop oracle.
;
; ⚠ VALIDATE-IN-CI: the exact init.srv directive set varies between LinFBB
; builds. This file seeds the identity the interop tests assume; after the
; first CI run, reconcile it against the `make installconf` default that ships
; with the pinned SVN revision (docker/f6fbb/README.md has the loop).
;
; The oracle BBS callsign + hierarchical address the tests expect:
;   F6FBB  with HA  F6FBB.FFPC.FRA.EU   (matches the transcript-suite dialect)
;
BBS  F6FBB
SYSOP F6FBB
HID  F6FBB.FFPC.FRA.EU
QRA  La Rochelle
; Home BBS hierarchical address components (continent/country/region used in R: lines).
TZ   0
; Mail/data and config trees (must match the Dockerfile PREFIX and the fixture MailDir).
PATH /opt/fbb/var/ax25/fbb
; Accept compressed (B1/FBB) forwarding — the whole point of the interop lane.
COMP 1
